<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Gingham | Home Decor for Your Dream Space</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --cream: #fffaf2;
        --butter: #ffe89a;
        --pink: #ffd8e6;
        --blue: #dceeff;
        --mint: #e9f8ef;
        --text: #4c4155;
        --muted: #7d7186;
        --card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
        --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
        --shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(160, 145, 177, 0.16);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Segoe UI", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255, 232, 154, 0.7), transparent 30%),
          radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(220, 238, 255, 0.9), transparent 32%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #fffdf9 0%, #fff6fb 45%, #f8fbff 100%);
      }

      img {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .page-shell {
        width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 2rem));
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .hero {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        margin: 1.25rem auto 2.5rem;
        padding: 1.25rem;
        border-radius: 36px;
      }

      .hero-panel {
        position: relative;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
        gap: 2rem;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 4.5rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 216, 230, 0.75), rgba(220, 238, 255, 0.88));
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 32px;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .hero-panel::before,
      .hero-panel::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        border-radius: 999px;
        opacity: 0.55;
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .hero-panel::before {
        top: -65px;
        right: -35px;
        width: 220px;
        height: 220px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      }

      .hero-panel::after {
        bottom: -70px;
        left: -20px;
        width: 180px;
        height: 180px;
        background: rgba(255, 232, 154, 0.35);
      }

      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.45rem;
        padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(173, 156, 188, 0.12);
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 1.25rem 0 1rem;
        font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.8rem);
        line-height: 0.95;
        letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      }

      .hero-copy p {
        max-width: 34rem;
        margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 1.08rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
      }

      .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.9rem;
      }

      .button {
        padding: 0.95rem 1.4rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--text);
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
      }

      .button-primary {
        background: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(171, 151, 185, 0.2);
      }

      .button-secondary {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
      }

      .button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 16px 28px rgba(160, 145, 177, 0.18);
      }

      .hero-visual {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .visual-card {
        padding: 1rem;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.52);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        border-radius: 28px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(173, 156, 188, 0.12);
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      }

      .visual-card img {
        aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 22px;
      }

      .visual-caption {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-top: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      .section-heading {
        margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
      }

      .section-heading h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      }

      .section-heading p {
        margin: 0.6rem 0 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .products {
        padding-bottom: 4rem;
      }

      .product-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 1.4rem;
      }

      .product-card {
        overflow: hidden;
        background: var(--card);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        border-radius: 28px;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        transition: transform 0.28s ease, box-shadow 0.28s ease;
      }

      .product-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-8px);
        box-shadow: 0 24px 45px rgba(160, 145, 177, 0.22);
      }

      .product-card img {
        aspect-ratio: 4 / 4.8;
        object-fit: cover;
      }

      .product-copy {
        padding: 1.15rem 1.2rem 1.4rem;
      }

      .product-tag {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
        padding: 0.45rem 0.8rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #fff;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }

      .product-copy h3 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .product-copy p {
        margin: 0.6rem 0 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.65;
        font-size: 0.96rem;
      }

      footer {
        padding: 0 0 2.5rem;
      }

      .footer-panel {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 1.25rem 1.4rem;
        border-radius: 22px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.74);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(160, 145, 177, 0.1);
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .footer-brand {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text);
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .hero-panel {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
        }

        .product-grid {
          grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .page-shell {
          width: min(100% - 1rem, 1120px);
        }

        .hero {
          margin-top: 0.5rem;
          padding: 0.5rem;
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 15vw, 4rem);
        }

        .hero-copy p,
        .section-heading p {
          font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .product-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .footer-panel {
          flex-direction: column;
          text-align: center;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="page-shell">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-panel">
          <div class="hero-copy">
            <span class="eyebrow">Soft maximalism for everyday spaces</span>
            <h1>Gingham</h1>
            <p>
              A Gen Z home decor brand that transforms Pinterest-inspired maximalist aesthetics into affordable,
              real-life products.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
              <a class="button button-primary" href="#products">Shop the mood</a>
              <a class="button button-secondary" href="#footer">Cute corners only</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-visual">
            <div class="visual-card">
              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505693416388-ac5ce068fe85?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
                alt="Pastel bedroom decor inspiration"
              />
              <div class="visual-caption">
                <span>Dreamy layers</span>
                <span>Butter yellow + blush</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="products" id="products">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <h2>Fresh Finds</h2>
          <p>
            Curated pieces designed to make your room feel playful, personal, and camera-roll worthy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="product-grid">
          <article class="product-card">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517705008128-361805f42e86?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
              alt="Gingham pillow set"
            />
            <div class="product-copy">
              <span class="product-tag">Best seller</span>
              <h3>Cloud Check Pillow Set</h3>
              <p>Soft gingham cushions in candy pink and cream for an instant bed refresh.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="product-card">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513694203232-719a280e022f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
              alt="Curvy pastel lamp"
            />
            <div class="product-copy">
              <span class="product-tag">New drop</span>
              <h3>Bubble Glow Lamp</h3>
              <p>A tiny statement lamp with a creamy glow that makes every corner feel softer.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="product-card">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505693416388-ac5ce068fe85?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
              alt="Pastel bedding and throw"
            />
            <div class="product-copy">
              <span class="product-tag">Pinterest fave</span>
              <h3>Sunday Layer Throw</h3>
              <p>Lightweight blue-and-butter knit made for bed styling, movie nights, and mirror pics.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="product-card">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1484101403633-562f891dc89a?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
              alt="Decorative wall art"
            />
            <div class="product-copy">
              <span class="product-tag">Room reset</span>
              <h3>Sweetheart Wall Prints</h3>
              <p>A playful print trio with pastel shapes that brightens blank walls in seconds.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="product-card">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494438639946-1ebd1d20bf85?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
              alt="Decorative storage basket"
            />
            <div class="product-copy">
              <span class="product-tag">Tiny-space hero</span>
              <h3>Bloom Storage Basket</h3>
              <p>Pretty woven storage that keeps your essentials tucked away without looking basic.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="product-card">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505693416388-ac5ce068fe85?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
              alt="Pastel bedside styling"
            />
            <div class="product-copy">
              <span class="product-tag">Styled set</span>
              <h3>Daydream Bedside Edit</h3>
              <p>Mix-and-match decor accents that give your nightstand a polished but cozy vibe.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer id="footer">
        <div class="footer-panel">
          <span class="footer-brand">Gingham</span>
          <span>Home decor for soft, colorful, personality-filled spaces.</span>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
